{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MIDIConnectionEvent","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_MIDI_API\">Web MIDI API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent\"><code>MIDIConnectionEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>构造函数</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent/MIDIConnectionEvent\"><code>MIDIConnectionEvent()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent/port\"><code>port</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web MIDI API 的相关页面</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MIDIAccess\"><code>MIDIAccess</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIInput\"><code>MIDIInput</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIInputMap\"><code>MIDIInputMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIMessageEvent\"><code>MIDIMessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIOutput\"><code>MIDIOutput</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIOutputMap\"><code>MIDIOutputMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIPort\"><code>MIDIPort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/requestMIDIAccess\"><code>Navigator.requestMIDIAccess()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div>\n<p>The <strong><code>MIDIConnectionEvent</code></strong> interface of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_MIDI_API\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Web MIDI API (en-US)</a> is the event passed to the <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIAccess/statechange_event\"><code>onstatechange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> event of the <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MIDIAccess\"><code>MIDIAccess</code></a> interface and the <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>onstatechange</code></a> event of the <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"此文档尚未被撰写，期待你的贡献!\"><code>MIDIPorts</code></a> interface. This occurs any time a new port becomes available, or when a previously available port becomes unavailable. 例如，这个事件无论是在一个 MIDI 设备插入或拔出设备时都会触发。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"构造函数","title":"构造函数","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"midiconnectionevent.midiconnectionevent_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent/MIDIConnectionEvent\"><code>MIDIConnectionEvent.MIDIConnectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>创建一个新的 <code>MIDIConnectionEvent</code> 对象。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"midiconnectionevent.port_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent/port\"><code>MIDIConnectionEvent.port</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>返回一个 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MIDIPort\"><code>MIDIPort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 实例的引用，指明其端口是否已经连接。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"举例","title":"举例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://webaudio.github.io/web-midi-api/#midiconnectionevent-interface","title":"Web MIDI API"}],"query":"api.MIDIConnectionEvent"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MIDIConnectionEvent","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MIDIConnectionEvent/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"构造函数","id":"构造函数"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"举例","id":"举例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"}],"summary":"The MIDIConnectionEvent interface of the Web MIDI API (en-US) is the event passed to the onstatechange (en-US) event of the MIDIAccess interface and the onstatechange event of the MIDIPorts interface. This occurs any time a new port becomes available, or when a previously available port becomes unavailable. 例如，这个事件无论是在一个 MIDI 设备插入或拔出设备时都会触发。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","ot